! Complete Feature List

!! Tournament Management

* ''Dynamic Player Management'' - Add/remove players at any time
* ''Multiple Game Types'' - Support for 501, 301, 180, and Cricket
* ''Player Statistics'' - Track games won, average score, best finish
* ''Game History'' - Complete log with timestamps

!! Live Scoring

* ''Real-time Updates'' - Scoreboard updates instantly
* ''Current Player Indicator'' - Always know whose turn it is
* ''Undo Functionality'' - Correct mistakes easily
* ''Bust Detection'' - Automatic handling for standard games
* ''Win Detection'' - Celebrates when a player wins

!! User Interface

* ''TiddlyWiki Styling'' - Clean, professional tournament interface
* ''DXC Purple Theme'' - Consistent branding throughout
* ''Responsive Design'' - Works on phones, tablets, and desktops
* ''Touch-Friendly'' - Large tap targets for mobile use
* ''Keyboard Support'' - Enter key to record scores

!! Advanced Features

* ''Match History Log'' - Track every action with timestamps
* ''Automatic Statistics'' - Calculated in real-time
* ''No Server Required'' - Runs entirely in browser
* ''Self-Contained'' - Single HTML file with all dependencies
* ''Offline Capable'' - Works without internet connection

!! Technical Features

* ''WCAG Level A Compliant'' - Accessible to all users
* ''Valid HTML5'' - Passes validation tests
* ''Cross-Browser Support'' - Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge
* ''No External Dependencies'' - All CSS/JS inline
* ''Portable'' - Copy file anywhere, it just works

!! What's NOT Included (by design)

* Cloud sync (keeps it simple and private)
* User accounts (no login required)
* Database storage (runs in browser memory)
* Network features (works offline)

This keeps the application lightweight, fast, and private.
